    {
      "id": "section-stack-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 28,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#4361ee",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "🏗️  ADR-001: Tech Stack",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🏗️  ADR-001: Tech Stack",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "stack-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 158,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Decision: pnpm monorepo\nReason: Share types between API and\nweb without publishing. Single lockfile,\nworkspace-aware installs.\n\nDecision: Fastify over Express\nReason: Better TypeScript support,\n2x faster request throughput,\nbuilt-in schema validation.\n\nDecision: MongoDB over PostgreSQL\nReason: NoSQL = flexible schema for\nrapid MVP iteration. JSONB lesson\ncontent stored natively without\ntable migrations. Easy to swap later.\n\nDecision: Mongoose ODM\nReason: TypeScript interface binding,\npopulate() for joins, index management.\n\nDecision: BullMQ + Redis\nReason: LLM calls are slow (5-30s on\nRPi5 CPU). Must be async. BullMQ\ngives persistence, retries, progress\nstreaming for future Ollama jobs.\n\nDecision: tsx over compiled Node\nReason: Shared package exports .ts\nfiles directly. tsx handles runtime\nTypeScript — no compile step in\nDocker, simpler Dockerfile.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Decision: pnpm monorepo\nReason: Share types between API and\nweb without publishing. Single lockfile,\nworkspace-aware installs.\n\nDecision: Fastify over Express\nReason: Better TypeScript support,\n2x faster request throughput,\nbuilt-in schema validation.\n\nDecision: MongoDB over PostgreSQL\nReason: NoSQL = flexible schema for\nrapid MVP iteration. JSONB lesson\ncontent stored natively without\ntable migrations. Easy to swap later.\n\nDecision: Mongoose ODM\nReason: TypeScript interface binding,\npopulate() for joins, index management.\n\nDecision: BullMQ + Redis\nReason: LLM calls are slow (5-30s on\nRPi5 CPU). Must be async. BullMQ\ngives persistence, retries, progress\nstreaming for future Ollama jobs.\n\nDecision: tsx over compiled Node\nReason: Shared package exports .ts\nfiles directly. tsx handles runtime\nTypeScript — no compile step in\nDocker, simpler Dockerfile.",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },

    {
      "id": "section-frontend",
