    {
      "id": "section-frontend-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 465,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 28,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f72585",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "🎨  ADR-002: Frontend",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🎨  ADR-002: Frontend",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "frontend-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 465,
      "y": 158,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Decision: Tailwind CSS v4\nReason: CSS-native config (no JS\nconfig file). Faster builds. v4 is\ncurrent standard as of 2025.\n\nDecision: shadcn/ui\nReason: Copy-paste components, no\nvendor lock-in. Full control over\nstyling. Radix UI primitives for\naccessibility. Hottest component\nlibrary in 2024-2025.\n\nDecision: TanStack Router\nReason: Fully type-safe routing\n(route params, search params). Better\nDX than React Router for TypeScript\nprojects.\n\nDecision: TanStack Query v5\nReason: Server state management\nwith stale-while-revalidate, automatic\nretries, optimistic updates.\n\nDecision: Zustand (not Redux)\nReason: Minimal boilerplate for\nclient-only state (auth token, session\nstate). Redux is overkill for MVP.\n\nDecision: Vite over CRA/Next.js\nReason: Fast HMR, no SSR complexity\nneeded. Single-user app, no SEO\nrequirements. Simpler Docker build.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Decision: Tailwind CSS v4\nReason: CSS-native config (no JS\nconfig file). Faster builds. v4 is\ncurrent standard as of 2025.\n\nDecision: shadcn/ui\nReason: Copy-paste components, no\nvendor lock-in. Full control over\nstyling. Radix UI primitives for\naccessibility. Hottest component\nlibrary in 2024-2025.\n\nDecision: TanStack Router\nReason: Fully type-safe routing\n(route params, search params). Better\nDX than React Router for TypeScript\nprojects.\n\nDecision: TanStack Query v5\nReason: Server state management\nwith stale-while-revalidate, automatic\nretries, optimistic updates.\n\nDecision: Zustand (not Redux)\nReason: Minimal boilerplate for\nclient-only state (auth token, session\nstate). Redux is overkill for MVP.\n\nDecision: Vite over CRA/Next.js\nReason: Fast HMR, no SSR complexity\nneeded. Single-user app, no SEO\nrequirements. Simpler Docker build.",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },

    {
