    {
      "id": "section-hosting-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 875,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 28,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2ec4b6",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "🖥️  ADR-003: Self-Hosting (RPi 5)",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🖥️  ADR-003: Self-Hosting (RPi 5)",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hosting-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 875,
      "y": 158,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Hardware: RPi 5 8GB + SSD\nReason: Quiet, low power (~15W),\nalways-on home server. No cloud\nbills. Data stays private.\n\nDecision: No GPU / AI HAT\nReason: AI HAT (Hailo-8L) is vision-\noptimized, not LLM-compatible.\nGPUs require PCIe x16 + 75W+\npower — RPi can't supply either.\n\nDecision: Ollama + Phi-3 Mini (Phase 2)\nReason: 3.8B Q4 fits in ~3.5GB RAM.\nLeaves ~4GB for app services.\n5-12 tokens/sec on RPi5 CPU is\nworkable when requests are async.\n\nDecision: Async-first LLM\nReason: LLM responses are slow\non CPU (10-20s). BullMQ queues\nrequests. SSE streams tokens to\nclient. Pre-generate exercise banks\non setup to avoid per-request LLM\ncalls during lessons.\n\nDecision: Cloudflare Tunnel (Phase 2)\nReason: Free, no port forwarding,\nno dynamic DNS needed. Secure\nHTTPS without SSL cert setup.\n\nRAM budget:\nMongoDB:  ~300MB\nRedis:     ~50MB\nAPI (tsx): ~120MB\nOllama:   ~3.5GB (Phase 2)\nNginx:     ~10MB\nHeadroom: ~3.5GB",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hardware: RPi 5 8GB + SSD\nReason: Quiet, low power (~15W),\nalways-on home server. No cloud\nbills. Data stays private.\n\nDecision: No GPU / AI HAT\nReason: AI HAT (Hailo-8L) is vision-\noptimized, not LLM-compatible.\nGPUs require PCIe x16 + 75W+\npower — RPi can't supply either.\n\nDecision: Ollama + Phi-3 Mini (Phase 2)\nReason: 3.8B Q4 fits in ~3.5GB RAM.\nLeaves ~4GB for app services.\n5-12 tokens/sec on RPi5 CPU is\nworkable when requests are async.\n\nDecision: Async-first LLM\nReason: LLM responses are slow\non CPU (10-20s). BullMQ queues\nrequests. SSE streams tokens to\nclient. Pre-generate exercise banks\non setup to avoid per-request LLM\ncalls during lessons.\n\nDecision: Cloudflare Tunnel (Phase 2)\nReason: Free, no port forwarding,\nno dynamic DNS needed. Secure\nHTTPS without SSL cert setup.\n\nRAM budget:\nMongoDB:  ~300MB\nRedis:     ~50MB\nAPI (tsx): ~120MB\nOllama:   ~3.5GB (Phase 2)\nNginx:     ~10MB\nHeadroom: ~3.5GB",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },

    {
      "id": "section-learning",
      "type": "rectangle",
