      "text": "🔄  ADR-005: System Architecture",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🔄  ADR-005: System Architecture",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "arch-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 675,
      "y": 708,
      "width": 550,
      "height": 390,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "Request flow:\n  Browser → Nginx :80 → [static files OR proxy /api/* → Fastify :3001]\n  Fastify → Mongoose → MongoDB :27017\n  Fastify → BullMQ → Redis :6379\n  BullMQ workers → Ollama :11434 (Phase 2)\n\nAuth flow:\n  Login → JWT access token (15min) in response body\n          + refresh token (7days) in httpOnly cookie\n  Axios interceptor auto-refreshes on 401\n  Refresh → new access token, rotate refresh token\n\nSRS flow:\n  Registration → auto-create SRSCard for every vocab item (status: new)\n  GET /srs/due → SM-2 query: dueDate ≤ now, sorted by due date\n  POST /srs/review → recalculate interval/easeFactor, save history,\n                     award XP if status transitions to review/mastered\n\nLLM flow (Phase 2):\n  API handler → enqueue BullMQ job → return { jobId }\n  Client polls GET /jobs/:id OR opens SSE stream\n  Worker → Ollama streaming API → forwards tokens via SSE\n  On completion → parse errors, store in DB, check achievements\n\nDecision: Nginx serves React SPA + proxies /api\nReason: Single port (80) externally. Nginx handles static\nasset caching, gzip, SPA fallback to index.html. No separate\nCDN needed for self-hosted deployment.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Request flow:\n  Browser → Nginx :80 → [static files OR proxy /api/* → Fastify :3001]\n  Fastify → Mongoose → MongoDB :27017\n  Fastify → BullMQ → Redis :6379\n  BullMQ workers → Ollama :11434 (Phase 2)\n\nAuth flow:\n  Login → JWT access token (15min) in response body\n          + refresh token (7days) in httpOnly cookie\n  Axios interceptor auto-refreshes on 401\n  Refresh → new access token, rotate refresh token\n\nSRS flow:\n  Registration → auto-create SRSCard for every vocab item (status: new)\n  GET /srs/due → SM-2 query: dueDate ≤ now, sorted by due date\n  POST /srs/review → recalculate interval/easeFactor, save history,\n                     award XP if status transitions to review/mastered\n\nLLM flow (Phase 2):\n  API handler → enqueue BullMQ job → return { jobId }\n  Client polls GET /jobs/:id OR opens SSE stream\n  Worker → Ollama streaming API → forwards tokens via SSE\n  On completion → parse errors, store in DB, check achievements\n\nDecision: Nginx serves React SPA + proxies /api\nReason: Single port (80) externally. Nginx handles static\nasset caching, gzip, SPA fallback to index.html. No separate\nCDN needed for self-hosted deployment.",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },

