    {
      "id": "rejected-postgres-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 55,
      "y": 1210,
      "width": 255,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#888",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "PostgreSQL\n\nWhy rejected: Requires schema\nmigrations for every lesson\ncontent structure change.\nDRIZZLE ORM adds complexity.\nJSON lesson content needs\nJSONB columns — gives NoSQL\nflexibility but with relational\ncomplexity. MongoDB is\ncleaner for this data shape.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "PostgreSQL\n\nWhy rejected: Requires schema\nmigrations for every lesson\ncontent structure change.\nDRIZZLE ORM adds complexity.\nJSON lesson content needs\nJSONB columns — gives NoSQL\nflexibility but with relational\ncomplexity. MongoDB is\ncleaner for this data shape.",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },

    {
      "id": "rejected-jetson",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 345,
      "y": 1200,
      "width": 285,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
