      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "rejected-jetson-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 360,
      "y": 1210,
      "width": 255,
      "height": 180,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#888",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "NVIDIA Jetson Orin Nano\n\nWhy rejected: $499 dev kit.\n8GB unified RAM (OS + GPU\nshare) means 7B+ models\nare tight. Mistral 7B at\n10-15 t/s — only marginally\nbetter than RPi5 CPU for\nsmall models. Not worth cost\nfor single-user personal app.\nUpgrade path exists if needed.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "NVIDIA Jetson Orin Nano\n\nWhy rejected: $499 dev kit.\n8GB unified RAM (OS + GPU\nshare) means 7B+ models\nare tight. Mistral 7B at\n10-15 t/s — only marginally\nbetter than RPi5 CPU for\nsmall models. Not worth cost\nfor single-user personal app.\nUpgrade path exists if needed.",
      "lineHeight": 1.4
    },

    {
