      "text": "Next.js\n\nWhy rejected: SSR adds\ncomplexity with no benefit.\nThis is a single-user app\nwith no SEO requirements.\nNext.js API routes would\nconflict with Fastify's\nbetter performance and\nplugin ecosystem. Vite\nbuild is simpler to serve\nfrom nginx in Docker.",
